**Corrupted (synthetic noise applied):**
```
... us abd: mild splenomegaly. otherwise unremarkable stduy of the left kidney and
spleen. mre: stable postsurgical changes as deascribed above. no definite mr evidence
of active infkammatory bowel disease. stble appearanec of pelvic oeritoneal inclusion
cyst. ... 05: 55am blooe wbc-4.3 ...
